üìö IF YOUR BUY / SELL ORDER ISNT GOING THROUGH üìö The pumps happen very fast . If your sell / buy order isn't going through , it is because the price has already changed during the time it took for you to place your order . Cancel it and place a new one at a new price . If you wait , the order may never go through . You might have to do this a few times , this is just what it takes to be in a pump . You must learn and execute the pumps well in order to profit . For example , if you attempt to buy or sell your coins at the current market price . By the time your order is in , the price is likely to have changed . Use your own strategy to buy above market price and sell below market price to ensure your order goes through . React quickly , study & learn from the pumps and you'll make profit .
